OL,18,FWakely (political), Richard Dixon
OL,19,F(industrial/economics), Tom St John
OL,20,FBarry (crime) and Gerald Seymour, Alan
OL,21,FHart, John Edwards, Sandy Gall, Richard
OL,22,FLindley (general reporters)."
